r may not go in is at castersrealm now at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/sol.asp.">eq.castersrealm.com/spells/sol.asp.</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
